   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improves the quality of living through access to safe drinking water</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To improve the general state of health in 12 villages in the municipality of Tapacar&#xC3;&#xAD;. This is done by constructing water supply systems that provide safe drinking water in sufficient quality and quantity, and by spreading knowledge of adequate hygienic practices through workshops and training of communal health promoters. In addition, the sustainability of the results of the previous project (42802301)is assured.</narrative>
